OL,3,CWoman returns from holiday to find
OL,4,Cbronze memorials stolen from garden
OL,6,FA woman from Midgham in Berkshire has
OL,7,Freturned home from holiday to find two
OL,8,Fstatues bought in tribute to her late
OL,9,Frelatives had been stolen from her
OL,10,Fgarden while she was away.
OL,12,FTerri Negus bought two life-sized
OL,13,Fbronze deer a year ago with money left
OL,14,Fto her by her late aunt and uncle. She
OL,15,Fsays the deer were a tribute to them.
OL,17,FBut when Terri returned home, she says
OL,18,Fshe discovered thieves had cut through
OL,19,Fthe fence around her garden to gain
OL,20,Faccess to the property and steal the
OL,21,Fdeer.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
