OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778666815
OL,3,CWoman returns from holiday to find
OL,4,Cbronze memorials stolen from garden
OL,6,FShe told ITV News Meridian: "(The
OL,7,Fstatues) had huge sentimental value to
OL,8,Fme."
OL,10,F"I'd actually bought them with a
OL,11,Flittle inheritance that my aunty and
OL,12,Funcle had left me and the same
OL,13,Finheritance helped us to buy our
OL,14,Fproperty."
OL,16,FShe added: "So because I wasn't able
OL,17,Fto visit their graves because of the
OL,18,Fdistance, that was my memorial to
OL,19,Fthem."
